snippet.title: Wolfgang's Channel
snippet.description:
Hi! My name is Wolfgang and I make videos about tech, Linux and computers.

The most reliable way to contact me is Twitter DMs – @notthebeeee
You can also write me an e-mail at the address below, I read all of the messages, but sometimes I'm too lazy to reply, please don't take it personally!

Brands and companies, please note that I'm NOT interested in promoting VPNs, online or mobile games, "privacy apps", Bluetooth headphones, CS:GO/Windows 10/etc. license keys and other similar products. The email inquiries concerning the aformentioned products or services will be ignored.
